docs.text: Welcome to Cache.bi Documentation For subscription service visit cache.bi . Introduction Cache.bi has been developed to assist end-users of POS systems review and analyse their sales, customer and inventory data in an easy to use and highly customisable environment. An easy-to-use Dashboard presents data to the user anywhere they are. Designed to be accessible on any screen format, desktops, tablets and phones, no matter what you are using to access our portal, you can see live, historic or analytical data. mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit.
